CKE Restaurants closes Hardee ' s acquisition . CKE Restaurants Inc said Wednesday it has completed the acquisition of Hardee ' s Food Systems Inc from Imasco Ltd . CKE said in a statement it paid $ 327 million subject to adjustment upon receipt of an audited balance sheet as of July 15 . The acquisition was financed by $ 104 . 1 million from bank borrowings and $ 222 . 9 million from a secondary offering of CKE common stock . 
